==English==
===Noun===
'''bittern''' (''plural:'' '''[[bitterns]]''')

# A [[bird]] of the family [[Ardeidae]] that lives in [[marshy]] areas, feeds on [[amphibian]]s, [[reptile]]s, [[insect]]s and [[fish]] and flies with its [[neck]] [[retract]]ed rather than [[outstretched]].

